Everybody's learnin' how

25:09.520 --> 25:12.400
Come on and safari with me

25:13.880 --> 25:16.520
Early in the mornin'
we'll be startin' out

25:16.560 --> 25:19.440
Some honeys
will be comin' along

25:19.560 --> 25:23.040
The next night
we went out with ammunition--

25:23.120 --> 25:25.520
Don't you have some homework
or somethin' to do?

25:25.560 --> 25:27.480
No sweat.
My mother does it.

25:27.600 --> 25:30.080
