26:06.920 --> 26:10.480
- Why did you do that?
- I don't like that surfin' shit.

26:12.240 --> 26:15.200
Rock and roll's been goin' down hill
ever since Buddy Holly died.

26:15.280 --> 26:17.520
Don't you think
the Beach Boys are boss?

26:17.560 --> 26:20.080
- You would, you grungy little twerp.
- Grungy!

26:20.240 --> 26:23.920
You big weenie.
If I had a boyfriend, he'd pound you.

26:23.960 --> 26:26.800
Yeah, sure. Shit!

26:26.920 --> 26:30.520
- Holstein!
- Good. A cop.

26:30.600 --> 26:33.000
I'm gonna tell him
you tried to rape me.

26:33.080 --> 26:35.800
I'm gonna tell him how old I am,
my parents don't know I'm out...

26:35.880 --> 26:37.680
and you tried to rape me.

26:37.720 --> 26:40.240
- Yeah, with shaving cream.
- Boy, are you up a creek.

26:40.360 --> 26:43.120
Come on. Really, Carol,
don't say anything.

26:43.480 --> 26:45.800
If you say:
"I was a dirty bird.

26:45.840 --> 26:47.880
Carol's not grungy.
She's bitchin'"...

26:49.360 --> 26:50.920
Say it. I'll tell him.

26:56.080 --> 26:59.400
I was a dirty bird.
Carol's not grungy. She's bitchin'.

26:59.480 --> 27:01.160
I'll think about it.

27:09.520 --> 27:12.640
- Where you goin', Milner?
- I'm goin' home, sir.

27:12.720 --> 27:17.240
- Where've you been?
- We were-- At the movies, sir.

27:17.320 --> 27:20.840
You didn't happen to be around 12th
and "G" about 8:30 tonight, did you?

27:20.920 --> 27:25.200
No. No, sir.
We were at the movies, like I said.

27:27.800 --> 27:31.120
I stopped you because the light
on your license plate's out.

27:31.160 --> 27:33.560
I'm gonna have
to cite you for that.

27:33.680 --> 27:36.960
And the front end
of this thing you're drivin'...

27:37.040 --> 27:38.880
looks a little low.

27:38.960 --> 27:41.880
No, sir.
It's 12 1/2 inches, regulation size.

27:42.000 --> 27:45.040
It's been checked several times.
You can check it if you like, sir.

27:47.920 --> 27:52.480
Look, Milner. Listen.
You can't fool with the law.

27:52.560 --> 27:54.520
We know that was you tonight.

27:54.640 --> 27:56.440
We have an excellent
description of this car.

27:56.520 --> 27:59.800
I could run you in right now,
and I could make it stick.

27:59.880 --> 28:01.640
But I'm not gonna do that.
You know why?

28:02.800 --> 28:04.640
I want to catch you in the act...

28:04.720 --> 28:06.800
and when I do,
I'm gonna nail you but good.

28:11.120 --> 28:13.200
Happy birthday, Milner.

28:14.160 --> 28:16.960
Thank you, asshole.

28:17.040 --> 28:18.920
You're a regular J.D.

28:18.960 --> 28:22.520
File that under C.S.
over there.

28:22.600 --> 28:24.640
C.S.?
What's that stand for?

28:24.720 --> 28:27.680
Chicken shit.
That's what it is.

29:00.720 --> 29:03.520
Ain't he neat?

29:03.600 --> 29:07.800
You know a guy around here
with a piss-yellow deuce coupe?

29:07.880 --> 29:11.000
- Supposed to be hot stuff?
- You mean John Milner?

29:11.080 --> 29:13.720
Ain't nobody can beat him, man.
He's got the fastest--

29:13.800 --> 29:17.400
- I ain't nobody, dork. Right?
- Right.

29:17.480 --> 29:20.920
You see this Milner,
you tell him I'm lookin' for him, huh?

29:21.040 --> 29:24.320
Tell him I aim to blow his ass
right off the road.

29:24.400 --> 29:26.280
Ain't he neat?

29:41.840 --> 29:45.200
What a babe!
What a bitchin' babe!

30:01.840 --> 30:03.480
Hello.

30:06.520 --> 30:08.240
You sure you don't
need a lift somewhere?

30:08.280 --> 30:12.240
You know John Milner?
John Milner's a good friend of mine.

30:14.000 --> 30:17.000
Did anybody ever tell you that you look
just like Connie Stevens?

30:17.080 --> 30:20.000
- You do. I really mean it.
- For real?

30:20.080 --> 30:22.480
Yeah. I met her once
at a Dick Clark road show.

30:22.520 --> 30:26.000
-Yeah? You really think I look like her?
-Yeah, no shit.

30:26.120 --> 30:29.760
