43:11.280 --> 43:14.720
- You met Linda?
- No, no. Hi, Linda.

43:14.800 --> 43:17.560
This is my cousin, Carol.

43:20.440 --> 43:22.560
I'm baby-sittin'.

43:22.640 --> 43:25.040
- Baby-sitting!
-Jesus! Watch it, will ya?

43:26.240 --> 43:29.600
Been hittin' me all night.
