45:04.760 --> 45:06.800
- Could you give me the time?
- Sure.

45:06.880 --> 45:09.000
It's quarter to 12:00.

45:09.080 --> 45:11.480
Quarter to 12:00.
Good. Thanks a lot.

45:16.720 --> 45:19.680
