I got a problem.

45:19.760 --> 45:22.520
See, I lost my I.D. in a food...

45:22.640 --> 45:25.400
and I was wondering,
since you're going in there anyway...

45:25.520 --> 45:28.000
could you pick me up
some Old Harper's-- hard stuff?

45:28.080 --> 45:30.800
- Would you buy me a bottle?
- Why, certainly.

45:30.960 --> 45:33.720
I lost my wife too.

45:33.840 --> 45:35.600
Her name wasn't Idy though...

45:35.640 --> 45:38.120
and it wasn't in a food,
but I know what you--

45:38.200 --> 45:42.040
Yeah, good. Here's some money.
Old Harper.

45:51.600 --> 45:53.920
- Quarter to 12:00.
- Right-o.

45:54.000 --> 45:55.920
- Night.
- Night.

46:04.120 --> 46:06.200
No, not wine!

46:30.280 --> 46:34.200
