- Yeah. Just went out the back.

46:34.280 --> 46:36.080
Want something?

46:38.760 --> 46:40.280
Yeah.

46:40.360 --> 46:43.000
Let me have
a Three Musketeers...

46:43.080 --> 46:46.680
and a ballpoint pen,
one of those combs there...

46:46.760 --> 46:48.560
a pint of Old Harper...

46:48.600 --> 46:51.640
a couple off ashlight batteries
and some beefjerky.

47:06.280 --> 47:08.400
