47:10.440 --> 47:12.120
Yeah.

47:12.200 --> 47:14.480
Oh, nuts.
I left it in the car.

47:14.560 --> 47:17.680
Sorry. You'll have to get it before.

47:17.760 --> 47:20.680
I also--
I forgot the car.

47:28.960 --> 47:31.960
Did you get it?

47:32.040 --> 47:33.240
You got it!

47:36.000 --> 47:38.360
You didn't get it.
Why didn't you get it?

47:38.440 --> 47:41.720
I needed some things and
I thought as long as I was in there--

47:41.800 --> 47:45.520
Look, Debbie,
can you loan me a dollar?

47:45.560 --> 47:47.480
